'''心理健康政策'''（{{lang-en|mental health policy}}）是一套有系統性的價值、原則與宏觀目標，其目的是用來有效改善一個國家或地區人口的心理健康狀況<ref name="ref4">{{cite journal|author=World Health Organization|title=Mental Health Policy, Plans and Programmes|year=2005|url=http://www.who.int/mental_health/policy/services/essentialpackage1v1/en/index.html|accessdate=2010-09-08|archive-date=2013-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131028142759/http://www.who.int/mental_health/policy/services/essentialpackage1v1/en/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
。政策內涵包括倡導、促進、預防、治療與復健等部份<ref name="ref1">{{cite journal en |last=Zolnierek |first= C. D. |title= Mental health policy and integrated care: Global perspectives |journal=Journal of Psychiatric and Mental Health Nursing |volume=15 |year=2008 |pages=562-568 }}</ref>，並會受到心理健康及疾病的概念化、社經脈絡、政治氛圍、服務結構、資源與治療的影響<ref name="ref2">{{cite book |last= Morrall |first= Peter |coauthors= Mike Hazelton|title= ''Mental Health: Global Policies and Human Rights'' |url= https://archive.org/details/mentalhealthglob0000unse |publisher= Whurr Publishers] |year= 2004 |isbn= 1-86156-388-4 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last= Jenkins |first= Rachel |coauthors= Andrew McCulloch, Lynne Friedli, Camilla Parker|title= ''Developing a National Mental Health Policy'' |publisher= Psychology Press Ltd] |year= 2002 |isbn= 1-84169-295-6 }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last= Lester |first= Helen |coauthors= Jon Glasby |title= ''Mental Health Policy and Practice'' |publisher= Palgrave Macmillan] |year= 2010 |isbn= 0-230-58475-6 }}</ref>。」

